            Volker Blum, Ralf Gehrke, Felix Hanke, Paula Havu,
            Ville Havu, Xinguo Ren, Karsten Reuter, and Matthias Scheffler,
            'Ab Initio Molecular Simulations with Numeric Atom-Centered Orbitals',
